m with two white towels hanging by the shower.', 'id': 0, 'negative_caption': 'White bathroom with two blue towels hanging by the shower.', 'caption2': 'The bathroom is blue and has two white towels hanging by the shower.', 'filename': '000000565045.jpg'}\nsplit replace_relation sample {'caption': 'A white with red striped bus drives down the slow lane on a freeway surrounded by several other cars.', 'id': 0, 'negative_caption': 'A white with red striped bus is stuck in the slow lane on a freeway surrounded by several other cars.', 'caption2': 'A white bus with red stripes drives in the slow lane on the freeway surrounded by various other cars.', 'filename': '000000460347.jpg'}\n","exit_code":0,"status":"completed"}}
